                "invention-title": [
                    "Angle adjusting device for cylinder valve of gas cylinder",
                    "气瓶瓶阀角度调整装置"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to an angle adjusting device for a cylinder valve of a gas cylinder. The angle adjusting device comprises a rack, a supporting mechanism, a transmission mechanism, a translation mechanism, a distance detection mechanism and a visual identification mechanism. A supporting groove with an upward opening is formed in the supporting mechanism. The transmission mechanism is used for driving the gas cylinder to rotate in the circumferential direction so as to adjust the cylinder valve position of the gas cylinder. The translation mechanism is movably arranged on the rack. And the distance detection mechanism is arranged on the translation mechanism in a lifting manner and is used for detecting the axial length of the gas cylinder. And the visual identification mechanism is arranged on the translation mechanism in a lifting manner and is used for identifying the cylinder valve position of the gas cylinder. And the gas cylinders with different sizes and lengths can be stably supported through the supporting mechanism, and the compatibility and practicability of the device are improved. Through the translation mechanism, the distance detection mechanism and the visual identification mechanism, positioning detection and identification of gas cylinders with different sizes and lengths can be realized. The angle of the cylinder valve can be automatically adjusted by matching with a transmission mechanism, accuracy of the angle of the cylinder valve is guaranteed, and labor cost is reduced."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及一种气瓶瓶阀角度调整装置，包括机架、支撑机构、传动机构、平移机构、距离检测机构和视觉识别机构。支撑机构形成有开口向上的支撑槽。传动机构用于带动气瓶沿周向转动，以调整气瓶的瓶阀位置。平移机构可移动地设置在机架上。距离检测机构可升降地设置在平移机构上，用于检测气瓶沿轴向的长度。视觉识别机构可升降地设置在平移机构上，用于识别气瓶的瓶阀位置。通过支撑机构可实现对不同尺寸、长度的气瓶的稳定支撑，提高装置的兼容性和实用性。通过平移机构、距离检测机构和视觉识别机构可实现对不同尺寸、长度的气瓶的定位检测和识别。配合传动机构可自动调整瓶阀的角度，保证瓶阀角度的准确，降低人工成本。"
                }
            ]
